{"tid":1936504,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"亞馬遜股價2023年將升至5,000元","createTime":"2020-03-21T09:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T09:55:29.000Z","uid":275872,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"247b979b729e05ab4bf660879048481d95b02ceb","tid":1936504,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:14:20.000Z","msg":"電子商務巨企亞馬遜(NASDAQ:AMZN)可謂這輪長期升勢的最大受惠者之一。自2009年3月大市見底至2月13日，亞馬遜股價的升幅已近3,500%，每股接近2,150元。是到近日才跌，但跌幅相對較很多美股溫和。<br />\n<br />\n事實是，即使於早前高位每股2,150元的價格對亞馬遜來說仍算非常「抵買」。表面上看，這雖然似乎過於樂觀，甚至近乎瘋狂，但筆者相信，到2023年，亞馬遜的股價能夠升至5,000元。若升至此價位，亞馬遜的估值便會達到近2.5萬億，成為全球市值最高的上市公司。"},{"pid":"74b67c76a44e8029e36a5f603036860025b204f9","tid":1936504,"uid":275872,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:14:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://yns.page.link/kqKFX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyns.page.link%2FkqKFX&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F9%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=0a68f1a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://yns.page.link/kqKFX</a>"},{"pid":"0585e90feb84f786e633120d1c19473c07511bb3","tid":1936504,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:16:31.000Z","msg":"1,846.09 USD &minus;34.84 (1.85%)<br />\n已收市: 3月20日 下午7:58 [EDT] &middot; 免責聲明<br />\n收市後價格 1,830.10 &minus;15.99 (0.87%)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a04534997c63429f69770722f1b7026c92901a","tid":1936504,"uid":208376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:17:36.000Z","msg":"alphabet 定google值錢d"},{"pid":"55a2f81dbd598ff16064a20b55b5e18600e730b8","tid":1936504,"uid":170335,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T09:19:15.000Z","msg":"今次肺炎加速左線上消費同娛樂 <br />\namazon Netflix 都好硬淨"},{"pid":"92631449143768db335a33673f99085659029d07","tid":1936504,"uid":310914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51a04534997c63429f69770722f1b7026c92901a","tid":1936504,"uid"